name: JJ Redick
bio: Dad. Husband. Retired NBA player. On TV sometimes. Interstellar. Golf. Wine. Co-founder @threefourtwoproductions. Host @theoldmanandthethree podcast.

Finally did it.  Broke 80 today for the first time.  Missed this birdie putt on 18 but cleaned it up for par to finish with 78.  Thanks to my guy Ryan (2nd slide) who has caddied for me the last 2 years and has seen nearly every shot- the good, the bad, and the confounding (the ones that makes you wanna quit golf).
 Golf is hard.  But I love it.
Happy 7th Birthday to our wonderful Kai.  You make our lives full of joy and laughter and amazement.  I can’t believe how much time flies.  4th slide is a few months after we moved to Brooklyn.

Happy 9th Birthday to our sweet Knox.  Getting to coach you this year in 🏀 and watching your passion for the game grow has been one of the greatest joys of my life.  You make every day better.  And I love that you love Tatum lol.
